cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving machine translation for resource-poor languages. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel approach for improving machine translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the accuracy of translation, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of statistical methods for machine translation.
